Class NotepadPPIconPack

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.hw11.jnotepadpp.icons.NotepadPPIconPack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IconPack

    public class NotepadPPIconPack
extends java.lang.Object
implements IconPack
    Special kind of IconPack used with JNotepadPP implementing Notepad. Provides all icons used by that program.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Juraj Pejnovic
    See Also:
    JNotepadPP, IconPack
